room_title: Escape room "Mosi's Curse" by Escape This in Hesperia
room_address: 10178 I Ave Suite D Hesperia, CA 92345
room_description: You and your group are in quite a predicament! A tomb raider was just caught and is rambling about a curse that has been triggered. A curse that is sure to destroy humankind as we know it. You have 60 minutes to stop it, there is no time to waste. Your group is our only chance! You must solve the puzzles and stop the curse before it's too late.
